Children.RevisionText:
REV B

REVISED FROM D83220P TO D83220/D83614/L3351182 AND FROM D83221P TO D83221/D83613/L3351183 TO Ref Des AT STA 728. REMOVED A STONE SOUP TOOL ERROR NOTE.

REV A

A STONE SOUP TOOL ERROR IS PREVENTING THE TABLES FROM ACCURATELY SHOWING THE STATION LOCATION OF DR3 AFT GI LIGHTS WHICH ARE LOCATED AT STA 1401+120. A NOTE HAS BEEN ADDED TO THE LAYOUT UNTIL A TOOL FIX IS AVAILABLE.

REVISED Description from WCU - DR2 Exit Locator, CrtnTrk - Bin to WCU - DR3 Exit Locator, CrtnTrk - Bin at STA 1255.
